name: THE TICKLE - Issue #20
description:
Art zine focused on Hic et Nunc artists and writers. 

Issue #20 features Liam Egan, Mumu the Stan & Luciana Yovine. Featured writer this week is meta-concrete poet Andrew David Baron.

Created by artists Wily Guys (@guyswily) and Maia Mellier (@maiamellier)
